{"tid":550722,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"楊受成送阿嬌750萬物業做嫁妝","createTime":"2018-02-05T04:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T07:14:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":112,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"646d1c92bcec5d7909d1bec231ae3eea2503814f","tid":550722,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:25:37.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】阿嬌（鍾欣潼）於農曆生日凌晨時分於微博上載閃爆鑽戒，並留言說：「下一站幸福」，公布男友賴弘國求婚成功的喜訊，其後阿嬌在接受訪問時指婚期仍未落實，不過昨日有報道指她將於今年內出嫁。<br />\n<br />\n至於老闆楊受成除了豪氣包下酒席及送上龍鳳 之外，還答應送一層價值750萬的上海物業給阿嬌做嫁妝，而這個過千呎單位更是一個智能家居，除了指紋門鎖外，還可以透過手機App操控燈光、窗簾及設置電梯到達時間等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8ubYPePWTymXhTBSUzP0_w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9MTAwMDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/D04c_ENP03P08050218copy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F8ubYPePWTymXhTBSUzP0_w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9MTAwMDtpbD1wbGFuZQ--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2FD04c_ENP03P08050218copy.jpg&h=cc4c2103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A5%8A%E5%8F%97%E6%88%90%E9%80%81%E9%98%BF%E5%AC%8C750%E8%90%AC%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD%E5%81%9A%E5%AB%81%E5%A6%9D-221906333.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25A5%258A%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2598%25BF%25E5%25AC%258C750%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%25AB%2581%25E5%25A6%259D-221906333.html&d=bYT7YVXwPebIsydqvR%2FBuozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=97e70e98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A5%8A%E5%8F%97%E6%88%90%E9%80%81%E9%98%BF%E5%AC%8C750%E8%90%AC%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD%E5%81%9A%E5%AB%81%E5%A6%9D-221906333.html</a>"},{"pid":"6b9e55a2a756afec165db2733192ad3f63ff09f3","tid":550722,"uid":90839,"like":448,"dislike":5,"score":443,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:27:35.000Z","msg":"楊生其實對自己啲員工都幾好<img